      "created": 1777448912,
      "updated": 1777448912
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b7cf0000000000af0dca",
      "text": "[「あのときあなたは文句を言わなかった」という論法]の類似",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777448912,
      "updated": 1777448924
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b7d00000000000af0dcb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777448912,
      "updated": 1777448912
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b7e00000000000af0dcc",
      "text": "私はちゃんとあの時に文句を言った、なのにあなたは止めなかった。だからあなたが悪いみたいな論法",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777448928,
      "updated": 1777448975
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b8020000000000af0dce",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777448962,
      "updated": 1777449023
    },
    {
      "id": "69f1b83d0000000000af0dd3",
      "text": "これもダメだと思う[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777449022,
      "updated": 1777449022
    },
    {
      "id": "69f45c300000000000b2804f",
      "text": "\t例が強烈なので切り出し",
